                </button>
              </h5>
            </div>
            <div
              id="collapseThree"
              class="collapse"
              aria-labelledby="headingThree"
              data-parent="#accordionExample"
            >
              <div class="card-body">
                <img class="my-1" src="images/about2.jpg" />
                <br /><br />
                <p class="text-justify">
                  Lecture-tutorial-workshop methodology of teaching, which is
                  widely practiced in the UK, is adopted at Herald College
